import { colors } from "../colors";

export const BlockImg = ({ isActive }: any) => {
  return (
    <svg
      width="220px"
      height="190px"
      viewBox="0 -5 100 80"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <rect
        x="107.029"
        y="0.759705"
        width="33"
        height="143.103"
        transform="rotate(62 107.029 0.759705)"
        fill="#FF0000"
        fill-opacity="0.3"
      />
      <rect
        x="-19.3234"
        y="29.897"
        width="33"
        height="143.103"
        transform="rotate(-62 -19.3234 29.897)"
        fill="#FF0000"
        fill-opacity="0.3"
      />
    </svg>
  );
};
